@startuml
title 時序圖：場景啟動

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam wrapWidth 220
skinparam maxMessageSize 220

participant "Main\n:Node2D" as Main
participant "Camera2D\n:CameraController" as Camera2D
participant "ParallaxManager\n:ParallaxLayerController" as ParallaxManager
participant "FocusValue / StatusValue / LayerValue\n:Label" as HudLabels
participant "LayerSky..LayerForest\n:Parallax2D" as ParallaxLayers

Main -> Main : `_ready()`\n初始化主場景
Main -> Main : `_apply_hud_mode()`\n套用 HUD 顯示模式
Main -> Main : `_update_hud()`\n更新 HUD 內容
Main -> ParallaxManager : `get_offset_mode_name()`\n取得 scroll_offset 模式名稱
Main -> ParallaxManager : `get_repeat_mode_name()`\n取得 repeat_times 模式名稱
Main -> ParallaxManager : `get_layer_lines()`\n取得圖層摘要文字
Main -> HudLabels : render initial focus/status/layer text\n渲染初始 HUD 文字

Camera2D -> Camera2D : `_ready()`\n快取初始位置與縮放

ParallaxManager -> ParallaxManager : `_ready()`\n初始化視差管理器
ParallaxManager -> ParallaxManager : `_make_layer_data(...)`\n建立圖層資料表
ParallaxManager -> ParallaxManager : `_apply_modes()`\n套用目前示範模式
ParallaxManager -> ParallaxLayers : initialize label visibility,\nguide visibility,\noffset, repeat_times\n初始化各層顯示與參數

note right of Main
啟動階段重點：
- 本地初始化
- 控制器協作
- 首次 HUD 刷新
end note

@enduml
